FBIS3-38650 "drweu025aa_94015" FBIS-WEU-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 February 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Spanish Government Condemns Sarajevo `Massacre' LD0502201294 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1900 GMT 5 Feb 94 LD0502201294 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] [Passage omitted] [Correspondent Jose Luis Durante] This afternoon, via the Diplomatic Information Office [Spanish Foreign Ministry press office], the Spanish Government condemned the Sarajevo massacre as an unspeakable act of barbarism which provokes horror and indignation, according to the note. [passage omitted]
